releaseData.title: Evil EP
releaseData.description: College Hill presents the Evil EP: Five video game themed dubstep tracks drawing inspiration from the classic Resident Evil franchise. Sure to be a challenge for DJs, every track here employs a 7/4 odd time signature with a few even switching time signatures mid-song! RE1 is one of the oldest College Hill tunes to be released, completed at age 17 while in high school.
